Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:37.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So sit back my little pony and enjoy the show
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:41.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Welcome Ponyvillians
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:44.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll be the first civilians
