Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:58.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of the Great and Powerful Tri-i-i-xie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Trixie's travelled far and wide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:16.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Although before she came to this town where you ponies reside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You might find thi-is hard to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:22.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But Trixie fought an Ursa Major in the Hoofington streets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So Trixie stands infront of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:29.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She can perform amazing tricks that every pony can view
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:32.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And what you do Trixie can do as well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cause every talent you may have Trixie can cast as a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Welcome Ponyvillians
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll be the first of millions
