Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:24.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But Trixie could have fought the Ursa on her own if she'd tried
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Twilight may have saved the town
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But Trixie's still the most powerful pony around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Ursa Minor may be gone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:37.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But Trixie will be back again befo-ore too long
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And one day you all will see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:43.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The awesome powers of the Great and Powerful Trixie
